name: Instagram App - UI/UX Kit for Unfollower and Follower
description:
Meet the Instagram Companion app. Connect your instagram to see your unfollower, recent followers, who blocked you, and also who stalked you! This UI/UX kit is for educational purpose and also for your inspiration! Feel free also to edit the UI/UX kit since it's yours truly.


Disclaimer, do not use this UI/UX kit for your plagiarism monetization. Please get creative with your own way!
